{"sections":[],"kind":"article","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/AstronomyKit\/documentation\/AstronomyKit"]]},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/AstronomyKit\/documentation\/AstronomyKit\/MoonPhases","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/astronomykit\/moonphases"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"abstract":[{"text":"Calculate moon phases, quarters, libration, and lunar nodes.","type":"text"}],"metadata":{"title":"Moon Phases","role":"article","modules":[{"name":"AstronomyKit"}],"roleHeading":"Article"},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"seeAlsoSections":[{"anchor":"Moon","title":"Moon","generated":true,"identifiers":["doc:\/\/AstronomyKit\/documentation\/AstronomyKit\/Moon","doc:\/\/AstronomyKit\/documentation\/AstronomyKit\/MoonPhase","doc:\/\/AstronomyKit\/documentation\/AstronomyKit\/MoonQuarter","doc:\/\/AstronomyKit\/documentation\/AstronomyKit\/Libration","doc:\/\/AstronomyKit\/documentation\/AstronomyKit\/LunarNode","doc:\/\/AstronomyKit\/documentation\/AstronomyKit\/NodeKind"]}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"text":"Overview","anchor":"Overview","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/AstronomyKit\/documentation\/AstronomyKit\/Moon","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" type provides comprehensive lunar calculations including phase angles, illumination, quarter searches, libration data, and node crossings.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":2,"text":"Phase Angle","anchor":"Phase-Angle","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The phase angle indicates the Moon’s position in its cycle:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["let angle = try Moon.phaseAngle(at: .now)","print(\"Phase angle: \\(angle)°\")","\/\/ 0° = New Moon, 90° = First Quarter, 180° = Full, 270° = Third Quarter"]},{"level":2,"text":"Phase Names and Emoji","anchor":"Phase-Names-and-Emoji","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Convert angles to human-readable descriptions:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["let angle = try Moon.phaseAngle(at: .now)","","print(Moon.phaseName(for: angle))  \/\/ \"Waxing Gibbous\"","print(Moon.emoji(for: angle))      \/\/ \"🌔\""]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The eight phase names:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"New Moon (🌑)"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Waxing Crescent (🌒)","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"First Quarter (🌓)"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Waxing Gibbous (🌔)","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Full Moon (🌕)"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Waning Gibbous (🌖)"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Third Quarter (🌗)"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Waning Crescent (🌘)"}]}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"level":2,"text":"Illumination","anchor":"Illumination","type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Calculate the fraction of the Moon that’s lit:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["let angle = try Moon.phaseAngle(at: .now)","let illumination = Moon.illumination(for: angle)","print(\"Moon is \\(Int(illumination * 100))% illuminated\")"]},{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Finding-Quarter-Phases","text":"Finding Quarter Phases"},{"type":"heading","level":3,"anchor":"Search-for-a-Specific-Phase","text":"Search for a Specific Phase"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["\/\/ Next full moon","let fullMoon = try Moon.searchPhase(.full, after: .now)","print(\"Next full moon: \\(fullMoon)\")","","\/\/ Next new moon","let newMoon = try Moon.searchPhase(.new, after: .now)"]},{"type":"heading","level":3,"anchor":"Get-the-Next-Quarter","text":"Get the Next Quarter"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["let quarter = try Moon.searchQuarter(after: .now)","print(\"\\(quarter.phase.emoji) \\(quarter.phase.name) at \\(quarter.time)\")"]},{"type":"heading","level":3,"anchor":"All-Quarters-in-a-Date-Range","text":"All Quarters in a Date Range"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["let start = AstroTime(year: 2025, month: 1, day: 1)","let end = AstroTime(year: 2025, month: 2, day: 1)","","let quarters = try Moon.quarters(from: start, to: end)","for quarter in quarters {","    print(\"\\(quarter.phase.emoji) \\(quarter.time)\")","}"]},{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Lunar-Position","text":"Lunar Position"},{"type":"heading","level":3,"anchor":"Ecliptic-Coordinates","text":"Ecliptic Coordinates"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["let position = try Moon.eclipticPosition(at: .now)","print(\"Longitude: \\(position.longitude)°\")","print(\"Latitude: \\(position.latitude)°\")","print(\"Distance: \\(position.distance) AU\")"]},{"type":"heading","level":3,"anchor":"Moon-State-Position-and-Velocity","text":"Moon State (Position and Velocity)"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Get the Moon’s complete state vector including velocity:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["let state = try Moon.geoState(at: .now)","","\/\/ Position in AU","print(\"Distance: \\(state.position.magnitude) AU\")","","\/\/ Velocity in AU\/day","let speed = sqrt(","    state.velocity.x * state.velocity.x +","    state.velocity.y * state.velocity.y +","    state.velocity.z * state.velocity.z",")","print(\"Speed: \\(speed) AU\/day\")"]},{"type":"aside","style":"tip","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Use "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"geoState(at:)"},{"type":"text","text":" for velocity calculations instead of